      "writtenOn": "2026-04-28T10:04:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Is there actually special code required here or is it just a bunch of target dependencies?  If there is special code can you elaborate what that is doing?\n\nIt seems to me on the surface that this could be handled exclusively through target dependencies, which you could install at a machine level (or via a meta-phosphor machine feature).",
      "revId": "b6dd3731158759f5c73a23828467024115fec41a",
